1
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:18,520
Move aside.

2
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:19,640
Everyone,

3
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,280
you haven't been cured yet.

4
00:01:21,280 --> 00:01:22,640
Why are you all leaving?

5
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:24,400
Divine Physician Ji treated my illness.

6
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,520
Since she is no longer at the Du Family Medical Hall,

7
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:28,240
of course I'm going to look for her.

8
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,680
We came specifically for Divine Physician Ji,

9
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:31,320
all the way from out of town.

10
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:33,440
Now that she is gone,

11
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:35,320
who wants to be treated here?

12
00:01:35,440 --> 00:01:39,240
Exactly. I've been taking medicine prescribed by Divine Physician Ji.

13
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:41,280
I don't trust anyone else.

14
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,560
Come on, let's go.

15
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,479
Oh,

16
00:01:44,880 --> 00:01:46,080
Auntie Zhang.

17
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,320
Please calm down.

18
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:53,039
Our medical hall also has the medicine prescribed by Dr. Ji.

19
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:55,840
You can take your medicine here with peace of mind.

20
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,800
Everyone.

21
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:01,640
My Du Family Medical Hall has been passed down for generations.

22
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:03,520
Our medicinal herbs are fully stocked,

23
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:05,200
and our medical skills are impeccable.

24
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:08,520
Please rest assured and continue your treatment here.

25
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,720
Dr. Du.

26
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,980
I have a minor illness,

27
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:14,840
yet you insisted on prescribing expensive herbs.

28
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,480
If it weren't for Miracle Doctor Ji...

29
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:20,120
I didn't know common herbs could cure it.

30
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,200
Oh my.

31
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:24,920
I've wasted so much money all these years.

32
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:27,020
I'm not getting treated anymore.

33
00:02:28,880 --> 00:02:30,280
Your Du Family Medical Hall

34
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,720
bullied us for being remote

35
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:32,680
and naive.

36
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,880
You've made so much dirty money in the past.

37
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,280
If it weren't for Divine Doctor Ji,

38
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,680
we'd still be in the dark.

39
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:38,240
Go.

40
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,720
Wait, don't.

41
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,079
Duyu.

42
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,840
I just had a dispute with Dr. Ji.

43
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,840
Get her back here right now.

44
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:52,800
But Father,

45
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:53,440
Dr. Ji...

46
00:02:53,440 --> 00:02:54,240
No buts.

47
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,120
She just left,

48
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,720
and business plummeted.

49
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,530
She has to come back at once.

50
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:02,880
Father, we must respect Dr. Ji's choice.

51
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:04,840
You bastard.

52
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,930
How dare you disobey my orders?

53
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:10,240
A concubine's son will never amount to anything.

54
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,640
Hmph.

55
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,480
Bring me the needles.

56
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,440
Mr. Shen,

57
00:03:23,640 --> 00:03:24,500
let me help you.

58
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:47,079
Mr. Shen, it's time to change Chuyun's dressing.

59
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,880
Duyu can't handle it alone.

60
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,680
Go and help him.

61
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:53,800
Miss Hu and I can handle things here.

62
00:03:58,720 --> 00:03:59,640
I'll go, then.

63
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,570
He's been poisoned.

64
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,120
Poisoned?

65
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:11,280
Sister.

66
00:04:11,440 --> 00:04:12,840
What does poisoned mean?

67
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:30,160
It's actually poison.

68
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,960
It seems the rotting of his fingers

69
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,440
was caused by the poisonous bugs acting up.

70
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:45,520
Father,

71
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,000
how are you feeling?

72
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:50,640
He is still weak

73
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,900
and barely conscious.

74
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,680
He'll be fine after some sleep.

75
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:55,720
Thank you, Doctor Ji,

76
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,320
for saving my father again.

77
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,520
You saved our whole family.

78
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:58,980
Please,

79
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,120
please get up.

80
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,120
It's the least I could do.

81
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,850
There is no need to be so polite.

82
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,440
By the way, I wanted to ask,

83
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,560
is there a house for rent nearby?

84
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:12,320
Dr. Ji, I happen to have an old courtyard house

85
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,480
at the south end of the town's main street.

86
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,520
If you don't mind,

87
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,800
you can stay there for free.

88
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,840
Absolutely not.

89
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,440
I must pay rent.

90
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:20,640
Dr. Ji,

91
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,340
you saved my father twice.

92
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:25,900
We can never repay you.

93
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:28,660
We just hope for a chance to return the favor.

94
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,360
Doctor Ji.

95
00:05:30,760 --> 00:05:32,520
Although this house is a bit old,

96
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,240
it's livable after a cleanup.

97
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,500
Please just stay here.

98
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,720
Thank you for your trouble.

99
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,450
No need to be polite, Doctor Ji.

100
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,720
You offended the medical hall for my sake,

101
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,200
and now,

102
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:46,130
you don't even have a place to stay.

103
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,920
I can't let you and Mr. Shen

104
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,600
sleep on the streets.

105
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,040
Thank you, Miss Hu.

106
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:55,480
I'll accept your offer then.

107
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:05,600
Chuyun,

108
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,580
your eyes haven't healed yet.

109
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:10,760
I heard about your quarrel with Master Du.

110
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:11,880
You were right.

111
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:13,640
Master Du went too far.

112
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,200
You saved me.

113
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:16,740
I can't just stand idly by,

114
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,040
so I want to do what I can to help.

115
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:22,120
Young Master Du also agreed to let me help you.

116
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,480
Your eyesight is poor,

117
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,120
and it's messy here.

118
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,380
Be careful not to fall.

119
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:29,440
I can see things vaguely now.

120
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:32,400
I want to do more for you, Doctor Ji.

121
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,720
I hope you don't mind.

122
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,280
How could I mind?

123
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,760
I can't thank you enough.

124
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,200
Besides, this is good.

125
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,400
You can stay here.

126
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:42,140
Continue treating your eyes.

127
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,480
I'll go back to look after my father.

128
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,540
Call me anytime if you need anything.

129
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,760
Don't worry.

130
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,880
We have enough hands here.

131
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,770
Watch your step.

132
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,920
Why are you looking at me?

133
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,240
We'll tidy up here in a bit,

134
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:27,770
and then come inside with me to write some medicinal herb lists.

135
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:38,200
I met the head of the Yan Escort Agency at the tavern today.

136
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,400
Yan Family Escort Agency.

137
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,320
That's the house you mentioned,

138
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:48,120
the escort agency where your old friend lived.

139
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,130
The head escort said I look like General Shen.

140
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:54,000
I've never heard of him

141
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:55,400
in my entire life.

142
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,720
Do you think this Shen

143
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,860
is the same Shen from my memories?

144
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,120
Be careful not to get conned

145
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,490
and end up counting the money for them.

146
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:08,240
That's why I'm telling you this.

147
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,440
Help me figure it out.

148
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,040
I think

149
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:16,920
you should stay away from Yan Quezuo.

150
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,880
After all, you don't know his background.

151
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,080
Okay.

152
00:08:24,520 --> 00:08:25,580
I'll listen to you.

153
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,920
Don't you think Yan Quezuo

154
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:31,720
is your chance to find out about your past?

155
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:35,120
Why did you agree without even asking?

156
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,559
Because I trust you.

157
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:49,680
But Sitai Town is quite strange.

158
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:53,160
The Imperial Court has banned poison arts,

159
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:56,480
yet poisons seem rampant here,

160
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:58,600
and everyone is accustomed to it.

161
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,840
Also, the patient I treated today

162
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:03,500
showed signs of poisoning by venomous insects.

163
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,460
Venomous insects?

164
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:13,440
Why did the silver needle change color?

165
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,640
She's poisoned.

166
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:19,360
And this poison is very peculiar.

167
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:23,400
It seems to be the same poison

168
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:26,210
found in the victim at the Prince's Manor.

169
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,040
Ji Bai, do you remember?

170
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:28,360
The Prince's Manor.

171
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,120
Physician Ji.

172
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,800
Physician Ji, are you in?

173
00:09:38,200 --> 00:09:39,000
Physician Ji!

174
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,240
Please help us!

175
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:42,120
What happened?

176
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,600
Take your time.

177
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:47,600
The Du Family Medical Hall refuses to sell us medicine.

178
00:09:48,040 --> 00:09:49,000
What?

179
00:09:49,400 --> 00:09:52,600
The Medical Hall is the only place in town to get medicine.

180
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:55,740
Even though their prices used to be ridiculously high,

181
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,280
at least we

182
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,140
could still buy medicinal herbs.

183
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,160
Let me see.

184
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,880
But now, Master Du says

185
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:06,880
that anyone you have treated or given a prescription to

186
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,920
is forbidden from buying medicine there.

187
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,240
This is simply outrageous.

188
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,400
He won't treat you,

189
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,800
and he won't let you see Ji Bai.

190
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,640
Isn't that driving you to a dead end?

191
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,160
You're right.

192
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,220
Young Master Shen,

193
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:19,520
we really don't know what to do now.

194
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:26,320
Maybe you can ask Young Master Du for help.

195
00:10:26,640 --> 00:10:28,640
I'm sure he'll help you.

196
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,410
Young Master Du?

197
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:33,400
Why would he care if us commoners live or die?

198
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:35,210
That's not true.

199
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,920
Young Master Du is a good man.

200
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,680
It must be because

201
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:40,760
he can't disobey his father.

202
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:51,200
Let me take a look.

203
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:57,780
How about this?

204
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,520
I'll draw sketches of some herbs.

205
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:02,040
Take the drawings and look for them in the mountains.

206
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:03,300
They are quite common.

207
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,640
If you can find some,

208
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,680
it'll help us manage for now.

209
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,300
As for the medical clinic,

210
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,850
I'll figure something out.

211
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,320
Thank you, Divine Doctor Ji.

212
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,200
Thank you.

213
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,960
Let's go.

214
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,760
Here.

215
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,680
Thank you,

216
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:30,880
Doctor Ji.

217
00:11:31,400 --> 00:11:32,600
Thank you, Doctor Ji.

218
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,480
You should hurry.

219
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,090
Don't delay the treatment.

220
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:46,920
It seems I need to go to the clinic.

221
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,440
I'll go with you.

222
00:11:51,120 --> 00:11:53,600
Chuyun, stay here for now.

223
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,360
Be careful.

224
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,960
Let's go.

225
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,140
Father, please have some tea.

226
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,970
Now you know you were wrong,

227
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,080
and want to come back.

228
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:25,120
Duzong, we are not here to return.

229
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:27,530
We have something to discuss with you.

230
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:28,440
Father,

231
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,080
Doctor Ji and the others...

232
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:31,240
Say no more.

233
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:34,920
If you want to come back,

234
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:36,880
just admit your mistakes.

235
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,440
I can let bygones be bygones.

236
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:41,840
Master Du.

237
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,320
We came back

238
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,920
to help the townspeople get medical care.

239
00:12:46,520 --> 00:12:47,580
Lives are at stake.

240
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:49,740
Please don't delay their treatment.

241
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:51,680
Oh.

242
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:58,040
Are you lecturing me?

243
00:12:58,720 --> 00:12:59,520
Don't forget,

244
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,880
you were the one who betrayed the Medical Hall.

245
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,680
Du Zong.

246
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,400
As a healer,

247
00:13:04,400 --> 00:13:06,000
you disregard the common people

248
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:07,400
and care only for profit.

249
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:09,000
Don't you have a conscience?

250
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:13,840
Du Zong.

251
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:16,280
We don't want to argue about who is right or wrong.

252
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:18,400
We just hope you can make an exception

253
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:20,720
and let them buy herbs at the clinic.

254
00:13:21,040 --> 00:13:22,160
Yes, Father.

255
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:23,680
Regarding this matter,

256
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:26,160
we should reconsider.

257
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,320
Shut up!

258
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:29,320
You scoundrel!

259
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,200
It's not your place to speak.

260
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:34,120
Head Du, you have the heart of a healer.

261
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,720
How can you leave them to die?

262
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:37,130
I'm leaving them to die?

263
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,480
If they really die,

264
00:13:39,520 --> 00:13:40,880
it's because of you.

265
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:44,280
If you hadn't betrayed the Medical Hall first,

266
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:46,410
how would they have ended up like this?

267
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,640
This is all your fault.

268
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,440
Damn old man.

269
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,170
I dare you to point at her again.

270
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:25,440
Yi Yi Nan

271
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:25,440
Wu Zhang Li Zheng Chen Luo Deng

272
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:27,100
Wu Zhang Li Zheng Chen Luo Deng

273
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,320
Xiaoxiaoxue Yiyinan

274
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,280
Ma Miao Lu Ran

275
00:14:54,280 --> 00:14:55,120
Ma Miao Lu Ran

276
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,080
Lü Sun Zhang Meng

277
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:00,160
Three.
